snippet.title: Velev Steam next fest Oct 2024
snippet.description:
VELEV - Exclusive Gameplay Showcase at Steam Next Fest October 2024!

Experience the groundbreaking fusion of MOBA and Extraction gameplay with our exclusive VELEV gameplay video from the Steam Next Fest October 2024!

🎮 First Look at VELEV Gameplay Dive into intense matches and witness the unique mechanics that set VELEV apart. 
See how strategic MOBA elements blend seamlessly with the thrill of extraction gameplay in real-time action.

🔥 Highlights Include:

Strategic Combat: Engage in tactical battles requiring skill and teamwork.
Extraction Mechanics: Feel the adrenaline rush as you loot and plan your escape.
Diverse Characters: Explore different classes, each with unique abilities and playstyles.
Immersive World: Journey through the mysterious landscapes of VELEV filled with hidden secrets and challenges.

👥 Join the Community Don't miss out on this revolutionary gaming experience. 
Wishlist VELEV on Steam now and be among the first to dive into the action when it launches!

Like, comment, and subscribe for more exclusive content and updates!

Steam Store Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2790930/Velev/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/KX9Yh3tQzP
